Qing dynasty

Events in the year 1911 in China.

Incumbents[edit]

  • Emperor: Xuantong Emperor
  • Regent: Empress Dowager Longyu

Events[edit]

  • Xinhai Revolution[1]
  • 29 April - Establishment of Tsinghua University
  • 27 April - Second Guangzhou Uprising
  • 10 October - Wuchang Uprising
  • 18 October-1 December - Battle of Yangxia
  • 20 October - Battle of Changsha
  • 29 December - Republic of China provisional presidential election, 1911

References[edit]

  1. ^ Fernand Braudel (1989). Gramática das Civilizações (in Portuguese). teorema. p. 201.
